channel.title: App on Fapesoft
channel.description: Recent content in App on Fapesoft

item.title: QR Scanner & Barcode Reader
item.description: The QR code Scanner app scans your QR codes or barcodes very quickly. The app has been designed to guarantee speed and efficiency in reading.

item.title: Sushi memo
item.description: Ordering sushi together with your friends at the table is easy with sushi memo. You can mark your friends' sushi orders in 2 modes.

item.title: 100+ Fart Sound
item.description: We are all eternal children having fun with the flatulences farts noise, so why not try this fart sounds app with more than 100 sounds of all different farts ?

item.title: Animal sound
item.description: Do you want to simulate the sounds of animals? Animal sounds app contains different sounds and hd photos of animals from all over the world, for everyone.

item.title: Bird sounds
item.description: Simulate the bird sounds, hundreds of different bird sounds and hd images await you. This app acts as a bird simulator, try them all and let us know which ones to improve!

item.title: Cat sounds
item.description: Cat sounds app contains lots of meow of different cats. This app is the best and most fun way to simulate cat noises.

item.title: Countdown Timer
item.description: Countdown, set a timer to all type of yours events in different mode, such as “123456 seconds”. Set a timer and receive notifications when the days expired.

item.title: Dog sounds
item.description: How many large and small dogs are there in nature? Dogs sounds app contains a large collection of dog verses, small and large.

item.title: Flashlight
item.description: The flashlight is a free, powerful and very fast app, it has been designed to open in a short time, in a flash, so as to allow you to have the bright light of your flashlight ready immediately when you need it, when the light is low.

item.title: Flashlight Application
item.description: Are you looking for a simple, fast and light flashlight that allows you to easily turn on the light of your mobile phone?

item.title: Invaders From Space
item.description: Defend space by destroying as many space invaders (normal enemy and Bosses enemy), as you can. In this arcade space invaders game, you are a airplane that sails in the infinite galaxy that seeks to defend the space by destroying the alien that appear to you in front.

item.title: Nature sounds
item.description: Shhhh, relax, listen to a stream, or the waves of the sea. Do you prefer to relax with the fire burning?

item.title: Never have I ever
item.description: Do you want to know what most people have ever done? Our game “Never have i ever” is designed for this!

item.title: Phone info
item.description: Do you want to have detailed information on your phone or device? Phone info app introduces you to your device down to the smallest detail.

item.title: Shark vs Penguin
item.description: Hey penguin, don’t let the shark eat you and dodge the crates! You are a penguin that runs over sheets of ice that appear beneath you at irregular intervals.

item.title: Sharky wallpaper
item.description: Do you want to turn your mobile phone into an live aquarium with a shark? Sharky live walpaper allows you to have your faithful pet shark directly on the background of your cell phone.

item.title: Simple calculator
item.description: Don’t you feel like performing operations by typing on the keypad? Perform your calculations with the power of your voice alone.

item.title: Url opener
item.description: Use the URL opener app to save web content. With URL app, you can save all the content you want, of any type: music video, link, url, news.

item.title: Would you rather
item.description: Are you looking for an addictive would you rather game to sharpen your mind?This is an amazing would you rather quiz game where you have to choose between two difficult and hardest choices.

item.title: Would you rather categories
item.description: Would you rather categories is a simple fun trivia word game in which you have to choose between two different choices and analyze the result.

item.title: Yes or no
item.description: Yes or no it’s a simple fun board game where you have to answer yes or no to a series of questions that are asked, easy to play, right?
